exthheader.author: Stephen King
exthheader.description: EDITORIAL REVIEW: From the depths of darkness, where hideous rats defend their empire, to dizzying heights, where a beautiful girl hangs by a hair above a hellish fate, this chilling collection of twenty short stories will plunge readers into the subterranean labyrinth of the most spine-tingling, eerie imagination of our time.
exthheader.subject: Horror tales; American.
